      "id": "8",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "1. Local Development Setup",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. **Clone the Repository**"
    },
    {
      "id": "10",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "git clone https://github.com/your-org/akira-docs-template\ncd akira-docs-template",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. **Install Dependencies**"
    },
    {
      "id": "12",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "npm install",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "13",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "3. **Create Environment File**"
    },
    {
      "id": "14",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "cp .env.example .env.local",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "15",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "4. **Configure Environment Variables**"
    },
    {
      "id": "16",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=your_api_url\nNEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=your_site_url",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "env",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "17",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "18",
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "2. Docker Installation",
      "metadata": {
        "level": 3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "19",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "1. **Pull the Docker Image**"
    },
    {
      "id": "20",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "docker pull akiradocs/akiradocs:latest",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "21",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "2. **Run the Container**"
    },
    {
      "id": "22",
      "type": "code",
      "content": "docker run -p 3000:3000 akiradocs/akiradocs:latest",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "bash",
        "showLineNumbers": true
      }
    },
    {
